overview: STIM, Isao Suzuki & Mamoru Ishida, Michiyo Yagi Koto Trio, Fumio Itabashi, Tri4th, Indigo Jam Unit, Chihiro Yamanaka & Hikaru Toho, Conguero Tres Hoofer, HB.  　　Description: Next stop on this journey - watch performances in a bike shop, on the streets or in traditional japanese houses. This episode contains also much talking from experts and musicians. The music itself crosses the borderline from jazz to traditional stuff sometimes.
title: Tokyo Jazzed Out
